1
00:00:00,000 --> 00:00:03,000
Two devices. One room code.
Call, Command, Control — in 60 seconds.

2
00:00:03,000 --> 00:00:10,000
Same room code on both sides —
tap Start camera.

3
00:00:10,000 --> 00:00:20,000
Hit Connect — live video, live audio,
peer to peer.

4
00:00:20,000 --> 00:00:30,000
Kid taps UP on the D-pad —
laptop receives the command instantly.

5
00:00:30,000 --> 00:00:40,000
Type a message, press Speak —
it reads aloud on the other device.

6
00:00:40,000 --> 00:00:50,000
Snapshot the moment, record the call,
done — no install, no account.

7
00:00:50,000 --> 00:00:55,000
Link below — lifetime updates,
works on any two devices with cameras.

8
00:00:55,000 --> 00:01:00,000
Call. Command. Control.
